# nine_and_zeros
Nine and Zeros 

//example

acherontas@raspberrypi:~/codeblocks/keno0_9_arm64/bin/Debug $ ./keno0_9_arm64 2785 20708050 22758352 15

eg 2785 20708050  29798959 15

2785 + 20708050 ::== 20710835

2785 + 22758352 ::== 22761137

22761137 - 20710835 ::== 2050302

22758352 - 20708050 ::== 2050302

20708050 + 22758352 ::== 43466402

20710835 + 22761137 ::== 43471972

43471972 - 43466402 ::== 5570

5570 / 2785 ::== 2


//

//example two

acherontas@raspberrypi:~/codeblocks/keno0_9_arm64/bin/Debug $ ./keno0_9_arm64 15722 1050712122 1959702020 15

eg 2785 20708050  29798959 15

15722 + 1050712122 ::== 1050727844

15722 + 1959702020 ::== 1959717742

1959717742 - 1050727844 ::== 908989898

1959702020 - 1050712122 ::== 908989898

1050712122 + 1959702020 ::== 3010414142

1050727844 + 1959717742 ::== 3010445586

3010445586 - 3010414142 ::== 31444

31444 / 15722 ::== 2
